bR‿bD‿bN‿bA‿bU‿bF‿bM‿bC‿bP‿bW‿bS‿bG‿bB‿bL‿bQ←↕∘≠⌾∾charGroups

Hex←16⊥(•d∾"ABCDEF")⊸⊐
MakeTab←{{(≠chF)↑⊑¨(chF⊐𝕨)⊔𝕩}○∾⟜(⥊¨∘⥊¨)´⍉(2(÷˜∾⊣)≢)⊸⥊𝕩}
